{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_11", "eventName": "淬火塵霾", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "11-2", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "一絲光亮", "storyInfo": "四年前，斯塔福德公爵在倫蒂尼姆城內掀起叛亂，混亂之際，戈爾丁救了負傷的海蒂。海蒂堅持要將情報送出城。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "32_g3_school_indoor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$path_intro", "key": "$path_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "四年前"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "1094年"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "3:25 P.M. 天氣/陰"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倫蒂尼姆奧克特里格區，聖瑪爾索學校"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 2.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿！看看議會廣場上的士兵們吧，看看那些弩箭與火炮，您已經無路可逃！", "name": "頑皮的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗚嗚......", "name": "天真的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別哭啊，你不該哭的，抬起頭來！你現在扮演的可是國王！", "name": "頑皮的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦......殺、殺了你們！我、我還有那些閣......閣樓騎士！", "name": "天真的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是塔樓騎士。", "name": "頑皮的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們大多投降啦。那些不投降的頑固分子，也很快就會跟您一樣，被我們和......我們所代表的，倫蒂尼姆的怒火審判。", "name": "頑皮的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰、誰能審判一個國王？", "name": "天真的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以前並沒有人，以後或許也不會有。", "name": "頑皮的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陛下，您是自尋死路。您擋住了維多利亞前行的步伐。", "name": "頑皮的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "整座城市的機器都因您的一聲令下而停止了轉動，您還想從苦惱的人們兜裡搶走他們買麵包的最後一個便士。", "name": "頑皮的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的雙手原本只是為了明天的太陽而勞作。是您和您貪婪的侍從們逼著我們......逼我們沾上您的鮮血！", "name": "頑皮的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上吧，戰士們！為了維多利亞！", "name": "頑皮的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞......！我......我就是維多利亞......你們豈敢！維多利亞不會放過你們，就算我變成了幽......幽......", "name": "天真的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是幽靈！幽——靈！你得先跑到那邊的台階上，然後倒下來，才能說這句話！", "name": "頑皮的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.5, "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.5, "delay": 0.3}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_657_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰在門廊這裡跑來跑去？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#8$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉爾夫，安娜，你們兩個小搗蛋鬼——", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是茉莉姐姐......", "name": "天真的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "馬上就到最好玩的地方啦！安娜，快跑到台階上，我們馬上開始絞刑！", "name": "頑皮的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_657_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "絞刑......絞刑？！", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#4$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是誰教你們玩這種殘忍的遊戲的？", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#4$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斜巷子裡的大人們都這麼玩。", "name": "頑皮的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_657_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斜巷子......那裡什麼人都有。你們是看到什麼不入流的戲了嗎？誰帶你們去看的？", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#5$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鞋匠湯姆。", "name": "頑皮的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他喝了很多黃色的飲料，很多從他臉上淌了下來。他還對著台上的人大吼大叫，說什麼“不許你們侮辱國王陛下，他是個偉大的好人”。", "name": "頑皮的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_657_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個混帳湯姆！不，我不該在孩子們面前表現得這麼粗魯......可是他怎麼能帶小孩子去酒館？！", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#5$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們繼續吧，安娜，在吃晚飯之前，我還想從頭再玩一次呢。", "name": "頑皮的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那該輪到你扮演死人啦！拉爾夫，你答應我的，不許騙人！", "name": "天真的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_657_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陛下呀......請原諒孩子們對您的不敬。", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#2$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們都未曾見過您，也沒聽過您的聲音，只從這些街頭巷尾的胡鬧裡聽過您的傳聞。", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#2$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "茉莉姐姐，你明明也沒見過國王吧，就別用這種老氣橫秋的語氣教訓我啦！", "name": "頑皮的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快跑呀，安娜，我來追你——", "name": "頑皮的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.4, "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.5, "delay": 0.3}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "xpos": 200.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "xpos": 300.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "xpos": 50.0, "fadetime": 0.6, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "xpos": 50.0, "fadetime": 0.6, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "滾開，叛......叛徒！你們遲早會被心裡面的野獸咬死！", "name": "天真的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_657_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "孩子們，這可一點都不體面。", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#2$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不想受罰的話，還是趕快停下來吧，可千萬別讓其他修士和老師們撞見......", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#2$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_657_1#2$1", "focus": 3.0}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "撞見什麼？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_657_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戈爾丁女士，您來了！", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#4$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#10$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉爾夫，你怎麼面紅耳赤的？", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#10$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，那是因為......因為......", "name": "頑皮的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們在做遊戲，女士。這個遊戲可好玩啦。", "name": "天真的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遊戲？", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#10$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#10$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，我知道了。早些回寢室吧，別忘了做今天的功課。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好的，女士。", "name": "天真的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有，拉爾夫，雖然茉莉小姐只比你們年長幾歲，但她也是你們的老師。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是，女士。對不起，茉莉姐姐——", "name": "頑皮的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了好了，聽女士的話，都回去吧。", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "32_g1_lentiavenue", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒想到您沒有批評那兩個孩子。", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉爾夫和安娜？我不怪他們。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#10$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "孩子們只是還未能理解什麼是殘忍。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們有渴望學習的天性。要是不能從書本和我們身上學到什麼是正確的東西，他們的視線自然而然會投向其他方向。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們......很多人都說那場絞刑改變了維多利亞。戈爾丁女士，您也同意嗎？", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#2$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "同一個問題詢問不同的人，只會得到不同的答案。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海布里區的軍工廠裡，機器從未停止過轟鳴，奧克特里格區的大宅子卻有許多換了主人。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我只知道每年依然有許多可憐的孩子被送到我們的學校裡。他們就和二十多年前的我一樣需要幫助。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感謝學校，要不是學校收留了我，我也早就得病死啦。", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "茉莉，剛才的事讓我有了個新主意。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "新主意......您是指這幾本您拿在手裡的戲劇集嗎？", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原來這些書本是為孩子們準備的。可是他們才剛剛認字，這會不會為時過早？", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#8$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總比斜巷子裡那些博人眼球，粗製濫造的東西要強。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對年幼的孩子們而言，扮演其他角色就和玩遊戲差不多。在理解複雜的含義之前，他們至少能先體會到些許蘊含在字句中的情感與力量。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但願您是對的。", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且還有一個好處，不是嗎？孩子們不會在我的文學課上昏昏欲睡了。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，這倒是沒錯。別的不說，只要能消耗一點他們的精力，我就也輕鬆多啦！", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#7$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside", "volume": 0.0, "channel": "a", "loop": "true"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 0.5, "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉女士們，書店得提前關門了。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "亞當斯先生，您今天歇得真早。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女士，您還沒聽說嗎？今天早上，卡登區的公爵辦事處發生了一場騷亂。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "騷亂？什麼樣的騷亂會影響到奧克特里格區？", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#10$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有一名辦事處的官員被打死了。據說他是斯塔福德公爵的侄子，一周之前剛剛進入倫蒂尼姆。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......可憐的人。警察抓到謀殺犯了嗎？", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#5$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "問題就在這裡。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有目擊者說，那個嫌犯逃進了城防軍的營地。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "StopMusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_soldiersrun", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241", "name2": "avg_npc_241", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快，封住這個街區！別讓那人逃了！", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "仔細找找——", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_657_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道那個嫌犯又逃到了奧克特里格區嗎？", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#8$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不好說，女士，事情可能沒有這麼簡單。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_657_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真奇怪，這些士兵是城防軍嗎？莫非我看錯了，為什麼他們身上穿著的制服和我印象中的不太一樣？", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#8$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女士，我有個朋友就住在卡登區，他說附近街道上出現了許多士兵，他們都穿著這種制服。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "甚至還有消息說......說......", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有一位公爵已經在昨天秘密進入了倫蒂尼姆！", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_657_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是這怎麼可能呢？這不是被法律禁止的嗎？", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#4$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "亞當斯先生，謝謝您，這些書太重了，我下次再來取。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "茉莉，我們得儘快回學校。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#6$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G7_decisivebattlealley_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒人？不是說看到有個影子藏在小巷子裡嗎？", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不能讓公爵大人的消息流出倫蒂尼姆！否則的話，今天的行動就......該死！", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "維多利亞士兵", "content": "連男女都沒看清，這些倫蒂尼姆辦事處裡的情報人員都是怎麼辦事的？"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "維多利亞士兵", "content": "一群飯桶！比公爵領的人差遠了！"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幸虧我剛剛射中了一箭——", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "繼續追，他應該逃不了多遠！", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_soldiersrun", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "32_g1_lentiavenue", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#7$1", "fadetime": 0.3}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#7$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "xpos": 300.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等——", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#4$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戈爾丁女士，您是注意到什麼了嗎？", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#8$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是什麼緊要的。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "茉莉，你先回學校，把孩子們都集合起來，別讓他們跑到街上。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那您呢？", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#4$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我要去見一位朋友。替我在辦公室裡準備熱水和一條乾淨的毛巾吧，我馬上回來。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "32_g3_school_indoor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔......哈......", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#5$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，請忍耐一下。學校的條件還是簡陋了些，畢竟孩子們通常只會在打鬧中跌倒，而不會被士兵的弩箭射傷。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#5$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒想到......你還會縫合傷口。", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#4$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每年學校收到的捐贈都很有限，我們雇不起那麼多人手。很多時候我還得兼職校醫。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗚嗚......疼......", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#5$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看你走在路上的時候一聲不吭，我還以為你感覺不到疼痛呢。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可別嘲笑我了......在倫蒂尼姆，只有來到你面前，我才能真正鬆口氣。", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#10$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只能幫你縫合傷口，卻做不到預防感染。海蒂，你最好立刻去醫院。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#5$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不行。", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#9$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#10$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能告訴我為什麼嗎？", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#10$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#10$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#9$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我以為我們是朋友。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我本來就不該跟你回到這裡。戈爾丁，我不想把你和你的孩子們扯進麻煩裡。", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#2$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#10$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，士兵們在追的人的確是你。他們真的是斯塔福德公爵的人嗎？", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#10$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#12$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#10$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是亞當斯告訴你的嗎？我以為他不會多嘴。", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#12$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#12$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "亞當斯是你的朋友，也是我的朋友。可別忘了，那場讓我們彼此結識的讀書會就是他舉辦的。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，我怎麼可能忘記？", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#1$1"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你當時可真是毫不留情。", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#1$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說我的新書是“被流行文化牽著鼻子走的媚俗之作”，“唯一的用處就是成為富家太太和小姐們茶會上的談資” 。", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#1$1"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我也說了作者的才華遠不止於此。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那時的我從未想過，整個倫蒂尼姆最有眼光的評論家會是一位默默無聞的老師。", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#10$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我能讀懂你寫下來的每一個句子，也能讀懂你沒有寫出來的另外一百句——海蒂，這是你親口說的。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我永遠不會質疑我們之間的默契。", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#10$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就讓我幫你。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#6$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海蒂，我們之間可以更坦誠......一如既往。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#6$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#9$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戈爾丁......我有沒有告訴過你，很多年前，我曾有幸認識了一位並非薩科塔的拉特蘭修士？", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#1$1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她也曾在倫蒂尼姆生活過，說不定與這所學校有些淵源。", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#1$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#10$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她是誰？", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#10$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#10$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她......", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#9$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_657_1#2$1", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戈爾丁女士，不好了！", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#2$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_657_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，您有客人？這、這位是......", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#4$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一位文學界的朋友。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "茉莉，有什麼事嗎？", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_657_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女士，外面......我以為您都聽到了......", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#2$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "StopMusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$grenade_explosion", "volume": 0.2}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_plane", "volume": 0.2}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_atk_stmkgt_h", "volume": 0.2, "delay": 0.4}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遠處傳來了一些異響。"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倫蒂尼姆人對這樣的聲音並不敏感。"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一開始，人們很容易把這聲音跟不小心引發的蒸汽鍋爐爆炸，或者孩子們喜愛的機械羽獸劃過半空的聲響搞混。"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 5.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$explolarge1", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rockhit", "volume": 0.5, "delay": 0.3}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$smallearthquake", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是隨著房屋與地面的震動感越來越明顯，所有人都被一種本能的恐慌包裹了。"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_battlefield_environment", "volume": 0.5, "channel": "a", "loop": "true"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_explo_n", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$corrosion_intro", "key": "$corrosion_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "仰賴諸王的庇佑，倫蒂尼姆從來沒有遭遇過天災，他們面臨的無疑是另外的威脅——許多年長者反應過來，二十多年前的噩夢又回來了。"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戰爭的預兆。"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 8.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_explo_n", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_explosion", "volume": 0.6, "delay": 0.5}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_explo_n"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就在人們沉默的間隙裡，轟隆聲更密集了起來。"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_657_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不明白。", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#8$1"}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是追捕幾個犯人，為什麼會鬧出這麼大的陣仗？", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#8$1"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是我們總能明白所有人的想法的話，許多悲劇根本就不會發生了。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#5$1"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "茉莉，麻煩你去看一眼街道上的士兵還在不在。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_657_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好。", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#2$1"}, {"id": 381, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "xpos": 200.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我必須離開了。", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#7$1"}, {"id": 387, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道。我很想勸你留下來，但我更加知道，就連炮火也阻止不了你。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 389, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戈爾丁，你也注意到了，今夜的倫蒂尼姆即將迎來又一次劇變。", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#7$1"}, {"id": 391, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯塔福德公爵的軍隊正在對議會廣場發起進攻。卡文迪許公爵的人也早就抵達了城牆外。", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#7$1"}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "二十多年前的那場政變，它所帶來的混亂，起碼對於市民們來說只持續了很短的時間。而這次......我不知道。", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#7$1"}, {"id": 393, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這可能會演變成公爵們之間的戰爭，而發生地點，就在倫蒂尼姆。", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#8$1"}, {"id": 395, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......先前取得了一些情報。它有機會拯救數萬人的生命。我需要在明天天亮之前把這樣東西送出城去。", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#9$1"}, {"id": 397, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#10$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你說，戰爭。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#10$1"}, {"id": 399, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#10$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恐怕是的。", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#8$1"}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戰火隨時會蔓延到其他城市，所有維多利亞人都需要做好準備。", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#8$1"}, {"id": 402, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自陛下離去之後，維多利亞的和平已經持續了二十多年。許多人把這稱作奇跡，而我早就不相信有什麼奇跡了。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1"}, {"id": 404, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有人會放棄利益，而如整個維多利亞那麼大的利益......則會讓有資格攫取它的人更加瞻前顧後。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1"}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "生活在歷史夾縫中的可憐人們，只好閉上眼睛，稱呼它為，“和平”。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1"}, {"id": 406, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#12$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵......誰能想到，一場急病會促使斯塔福德公爵邁出這一步？誰又能預測其他公爵對此的反應？", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#12$1"}, {"id": 408, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#12$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有像你這樣的人的付出的話，這場戰爭會在二十二年前就爆發，而不是拖到現在。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 410, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是想安慰我嗎，戈爾丁？", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#7$1"}, {"id": 412, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是在陳述一個事實。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 414, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海蒂，你不用向我說明你此行的目的，更不用解釋你們這麼多年來的計劃究竟是什麼。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 415, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你只需要回答一個問題——和平還會再次到來嗎？", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 416, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......會。", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#10$1"}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這始終是我們努力的方向。", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#10$1"}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們會守護自己的家園，這是維多利亞人世代信奉的真理。", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#10$1"}, {"id": 420, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即便會有無數人死在這條道路上，即便你們每一次以為自己即將到達道路的終點時，迎接你們的都是下一場註定發生的戰爭？", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#6$1"}, {"id": 422, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#10$1"}, {"id": 424, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為戰爭終會結束。它會結束在我們或者我們的後繼者的手上。等籠罩在維多利亞上空的煙塵散去，孩子們的笑臉上將再無陰霾。", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#1$1"}, {"id": 426, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那好。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1"}, {"id": 428, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海蒂，我願意試著相信你。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1"}, {"id": 429, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戈爾丁，要是我還能回到倫蒂尼姆的話......等我們再次相聚，我會把所有的事情都說出來。", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#10$1"}, {"id": 431, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_400_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "記住你的承諾。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1"}, {"id": 433, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......活著回來。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1"}, {"id": 434, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}